metadata.description: Sun, sand, swimsuits and cool rockin' tunes - no, it's not a cinematic 'beach party' blast from the past, but a whole new summer splash from Archie and his friends! In this fun-filled free issue, Cheryl and her snooty friends from Pembrooke form an all-girl group to compete head on with the Archies at a summer beach music festival. Will Cheryl's group be a tuneful treat, or mistaken for bellowing whales?
metadata.name: Free Comic Book Day: Archie
